916
00:36:13,501 --> 00:36:16,100
Take care of yourself.

917
00:36:16,102 --> 00:36:18,670
Well, I guess that's settled.

918
00:36:19,975 --> 00:36:21,039
So, let's talk about some changes.

919
00:36:21,041 --> 00:36:22,840
Shall we?

920
00:36:22,842 --> 00:36:24,509
From now on...

921
00:36:24,511 --> 00:36:26,811
I'm the face of the Marbella.

922
00:36:31,412 --> 00:36:33,545
To say that Petra was on
top of the world right now,

923
00:36:33,547 --> 00:36:35,613
