933
00:36:52,054 --> 00:36:54,724
Yes. Oh.

934
00:36:54,726 --> 00:36:56,127
Yes, of course you are.

935
00:36:56,219 --> 00:36:57,619
I'm sorry. Excuse me.

936
00:36:57,621 --> 00:37:01,192
